  "name": "Uzumaki Clan",
  "type": "feat",
  "system": {
    "subType": "trait",
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The Uzumaki clan was once a very prominent clan in Uzushiokagure. They are renowned for their talents in fuinjutsu, or sealing arts. They are also known to have a long lifespan and an incredible life force. However, it is rare to see an Uzumaki today, for their clan was almost entirely destroyed in the Third Shinobi War.</p><p><b>Source:</b> Mechanics/Character_Options/Occupations/Community Compendium/Uzumaki Clan.md</p><p><b>Category:</b> Community Compendium</p><p><b>Prerequisite:</b> Age 8+</p><p><b>Class Skills:</b> Select 3 from Balance, Chakra Control, Craft (calligraphy), Fuinjutsu, Knowledge (Ninja Lore), Ninjutsu, Sense Motive, Spot, Taijutsu, Treat Injury.</p><p><b>Feat:</b> Select one from Advanced Study, Chakra Restoration, Fuinjutsu Adept, Genin, Genius Nin, Improved Chakra Pool, Sealweaver, Skilled, Talented Shinobi.</p><p><b>Wealth Bonus Increase:</b> +1</p><p><b>Reputation Bonus Increase:</b> +2</p><p><b>Affiliation:</b> You are required 1 less success to learn Fuinjutsu techniques.</p>"
    },
